org.stringmatching.matcher

Interface IMatcher

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AC_Matcher, AC_WM_Matcher, Matcher, WM_Matcher

    public interface IMatcher
    This interface define the basic function for a Matcher algorithm

    For an input text the doMatch function must to parse the text (stream) in order to find all the positions in the text for a pattern/s To allow concurrence by splitting the text in segments, the start position is used to set correctly the pattern position in the full text.

    beetecu
